text: pour olive oil into a hot pan add
chopped tomatoes
spring onions and fry season next add
cooked prawns and a sprinkle of chili
flakes to give it a lovely kick of heat
cook through and set aside next beat
four eggs add olive oil to your frying
pan and pour in the eggs
sprinkled on freshly chopped oregano
which works brilliantly with eggs and
spoon over the spicy prawns crumpled
over creamy feta cheese and grill for a
couple of minutes
this is eggs to the nth degree
packed with different tastes textures
and flavors all working wonderfully
together perfect next add fresh chopped
tomatoes then cumin seeds and fry until
the seeds are fragrant and the tomatoes
are lovely and soft and then for extra
richness knobs of butter then butter a
baking dish and pour in your rich cheesy
cheats souffl√© mix
